Text.val: 31.08.2011 GB SCR16716 Added update the CCRY302_TYPEOFDUNNING value

SQL_STMT_U.val: select a.CCRY308_ADMNO, a.CCRY308_CLNTNO, a.CCRY308_COUNTRY from :1/CCRY a where a.CCRY308_COUNTRY = 'BE' and not (exists (select * from :1/CCRY where CCRY308_ADMNO = a.CCRY308_ADMNO and CCRY308_CLNTNO = a.CCRY308_CLNTNO and CCRY308_COUNTRY = 'YY'))

select a.CCRY308_ADMNO, a.CCRY308_CLNTNO, a.CCRY308_COUNTRY from :1/NCCT a where a.CCRY308_COUNTRY = 'BE' and not (exists (select * from :1/NCCT where CCRY308_ADMNO = a.CCRY308_ADMNO and CCRY308_CLNTNO = a.CCRY308_CLNTNO and CCRY308_COUNTRY = 'YY'))

select a.CCDU302_ADMNO, a.CCDU302_CLNTNO, a.CCDU302_COUNTRY, a.CCDU302_DUNNNO from :1/CCDU a where a.CCDU302_COUNTRY = 'BE' and not (exists (select * from :1/CCDU where CCDU302_ADMNO = a.CCDU302_ADMNO and CCDU302_CLNTNO = a.CCDU302_CLNTNO and CCDU302_COUNTRY = 'YY' and CCDU302_DUNNNO = a.CCDU302_DUNNNO))

select a.CCDU302_ADMNO, a.CCDU302_CLNTNO, a.CCDU302_COUNTRY, a.CCDU302_DUNNNO from :1/NCCD a where a.CCDU302_COUNTRY = 'BE' and not (exists (select * from :1/NCCD where CCDU302_ADMNO = a.CCDU302_ADMNO and CCDU302_CLNTNO = a.CCDU302_CLNTNO and CCDU302_COUNTRY = 'YY' and CCDU302_DUNNNO = a.CCDU302_DUNNNO))
